cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CY, cs.SD 

This paper deals with natural language processing and specifically focuses on gender bias in machine translation systems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also proposes a scheme for evaluating gender bias, which involves constructing word/phrase sets and additional sentence lists, indicating a possible connection to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also involves data analysis, which could fall under cs.CY (Computational Geometry) or cs.SD (Sound).
